| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2303 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 50f58ddc-c8d7-550d-938d-ca37e4e1b446"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
